Package: zfs-backup
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, zfsutils-linux, sanoid
Recommends: udisks2
Description: Beautiful TUI for managing ZFS backups
 A beautiful Terminal User Interface (TUI) for managing ZFS backups to external
 drives. Features include:
 .
  - Incremental backups using syncoid
  - File restoration from snapshots with dual-panel browser
  - Pool information viewer with detailed status
  - Pool maintenance with scrub start/stop/monitor
  - Safe device unmounting with power-off
  - Encrypted pool support
 .
 Made with <3 by Kartoza.
